<bibRefCitation author="Bousquet, Y" journalOrPublisher="Memoirs of the Entomological Society of Canada" pageId="11" pageNumber="272" pagination="1 - 397" title="Catalogue of the Geadephaga (Coleoptera: Trachypachidae, Rhysodidae, Carabidae including Cicindelini) of America north of Mexico." url="doi: 10.4039/entm125167fv" volume="167" year="1993">Bousquet and Larochelle 1993</bibRefCitation>
and Maddison, unpublished).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
